{"title":"Python炼丹炉（maching learning）环境搭建常见问题","date":"2019-01-31T00:00:00.000Z","link":"python/Conda","tags":["Python"],"updated":"2022-04-27T15:24:01.731Z","content":"<h1 id=\"using-anacondaconda-with-powershell\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"python/Conda#using-anacondaconda-with-powershell\"></a> Using Anaconda/Conda with Powershell<a href=\"python/Conda#using-anacondaconda-with-powershell\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>在anaconda/conda中创建虚拟python环境：<br>\nconda create -n env_name python=x.x</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在anaconda prompt 和 cmd中，激活一个环境：<br>\nactivate env_name</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Powershell添加conda/anaconda支持：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>安装库： <figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda install -n root -c pscondaenvs pscondaenvs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p>如果因为某些原因无法通过上述方案安装……请手动下载安装</p>\n<p>Offical Link： <a href=\"https://github.com/BCSharp/PSCondaEnvs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/BCSharp/PSCondaEnvs</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>更改PowerShell配置：<br>\n以<strong>管理员</strong>身份启动PowerShell，并执行<figure class=\"highlight\"><figcaption><span>RemoteSigned```</span></figcaption><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">``` powershell</span><br><span class=\"line\">PS C:\\Hanyuu&gt; Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">执行策略更改</span><br><span class=\"line\">执行策略可帮助你防止执行不信任的脚本。更改执行策略可能会产生安全风险，如http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=135170 中的 about_Execution_Policies帮助主题所述。是否要更改执行策略?</span><br><span class=\"line\">[Y] 是(Y)  [A] 全是(A)  [N] 否(N)  [L] 全否(L)  [S] 暂停(S)  [?] 帮助(默认值为“N”):Y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>此时可以正常使用Powershell切换到特定环境</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">activate [EnvironmentName]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>原理：其实……就是……加了个……ps1文件替换bat……（呵呵呵~）</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"using-jupyter-with-anacondaconda\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"python/Conda#using-jupyter-with-anacondaconda\"></a> Using Jupyter with anaconda/conda<a href=\"python/Conda#using-jupyter-with-anacondaconda\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>原理：在虚拟环境下缺少kernel.json文件</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add a exists environment into Jupyter</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Install ipykernel</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda install ipykernel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create kernel files in virtual environment</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda install -n [EnvironmentName] ipykernel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>activate virtual environment</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">activate [EnvironmentName]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add your virtual environment into kernel for notebook</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python -m ipykernel install --user --name [EnvironmentName] --display-name [EnvironmentDisplayName]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>open your jupyter notebook and enjoy your pythoning : )</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jupyter notebook</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>If your environment has not been created…</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda create -n [EnvironmentName] python=?.? ipykernel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Delete a environment</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jupyter kernelspec remote [EnvironmentName]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"jupyter-自动补全和主题修改\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"python/Conda#jupyter-自动补全和主题修改\"></a> Jupyter 自动补全和主题修改<a href=\"python/Conda#jupyter-自动补全和主题修改\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/qiuxirufeng/p/9609031.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">link</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"terminology in deeplearning","link":"Tensorflow/terminology"},"next":{"title":"Tensorflow卷积和池化","link":"Tensorflow/TensorflowConvandPool"},"plink":"ilucia.github.io/python/Conda/","toc":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> Using Anaconda/Conda with Powershell","id":"using-anacondaconda-with-powershell","index":"1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> Using Jupyter with anaconda/conda","id":"using-jupyter-with-anacondaconda","index":"2","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> Jupyter 自动补全和主题修改","id":"jupyter-自动补全和主题修改","index":"2.1"}]}],"copyright":{"author":"Ilucia Niu","license":"<a rel=\"license\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">知识共享署名 4.0 国际许可协议</a>","published":"2019年1月31日","updated":"2022年4月27日"}}